{#
  Narrative Template
  ==================
  Interpretive/qualitative structure: Field, Voice, Pattern, Insight.
  For interpretive and qualitative research traditions.

  Required Variables:
  - title: Paper title
  - author: Author name(s)
  - abstract: Paper abstract

  Optional Variables:
  - field: Research field description content
  - voice: Researcher perspective content
  - pattern: Pattern identification content
  - insight: Interpretation and synthesis content
  - date: Publication date (defaults to \today)
  - bibliography: Bibliography file name (defaults to 'references')

  Usage:
    const context = {
      title: "Narratives of Technology Adoption",
      author: "Qualitative Researcher",
      abstract: "This narrative inquiry explores...",
      field: "The research takes place in...",
      voice: "As a researcher positioned...",
      pattern: "Three recurring themes emerged...",
      insight: "These patterns reveal..."
    };
#}
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{hyperref}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{graphicx}

\title{{ '{' }}{{ title | texescape }}{{ '}' }}
\author{{ '{' }}{{ author | texescape }}{{ '}' }}
\date{{ '{' }}{% if date %}{{ date | texescape }}{% else %}\today{% endif %}{{ '}' }}

\begin{document}
\maketitle

\begin{abstract}
{{ abstract | texescape }}
\end{abstract}

% Narrative Thesis Structure: Field, Voice, Pattern, Insight
% This structure supports interpretive and qualitative research traditions

\section{Field}
{% if field %}{{ field | texescape }}{% endif %}

Description of the research field and context, establishing the landscape within which the narrative unfolds.

\section{Voice}
{% if voice %}{{ voice | texescape }}{% endif %}

The researcher's perspective and positionality, acknowledging subjectivity and reflexivity in the interpretive process.

\section{Pattern}
{% if pattern %}{{ pattern | texescape }}{% endif %}

Identification and articulation of patterns emerging from the data, weaving together themes and recurring elements.

\section{Insight}
{% if insight %}{{ insight | texescape }}{% endif %}

Interpretation and synthesis of insights, offering meaning-making and implications for understanding the phenomenon.

\bibliographystyle{plain}
\bibliography{{ '{' }}{{ bibliography | default('references') }}{{ '}' }}

\end{document}
